# React compiler output — regenerated by Railway on every deploy (nixpacks runs `npm run build`).
# Keeping these out of git removes the #1 merge-conflict source (hashed JS bundles).
# NOTE: build/audio, build/mockup, build/screenshots, build/videos and build/*.png are STILL
# committed — nixpacks restores them after the build, and audio's only git copy lives here.
